        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="context-is-king">Context is king.</h1>
<p>The essence of learning anything new comes to <em>context</em>. Context is king.
Contextualizing a subject is the way you can relate the subject or information presented to you as a method of learning it deeply.</p>
<p>If you wanted to convert any highly boring and theoretical information into that which is easier for you to understand and process, and retain it over a long period of time, then the idea is to put it into different contexts.</p>]]></summary>
    </entry>
